    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8 mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">What is a Confidence Pool?</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        A confidence pool is a type of football betting game where you pick the winner of each game,
        but also assign confidence points based on how sure you are of each pick. The game with your
        highest confidence gets the most points (equal to the number of games), and so on down to 1 point
        for your least confident pick.
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">How to Play:</h3>
      <ol class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-700 mb-4">
        <li>Look at all the games for the week</li>
        <li>Pick who you think will win each game</li>
        <li>Rank the games by how confident you are in your pick</li>
        <li>Drag and drop to reorder - highest confidence at the top</li>
        <li>Export your picks to paste into your league</li>
      </ol>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Features:</h3>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-700">
        <li><strong>Live Odds:</strong> Real-time NFL odds from multiple sportsbooks</li>
        <li><strong>Drag & Drop:</strong> Easy reordering of your confidence rankings</li>
        <li><strong>Auto-Save:</strong> Your picks are saved locally in your browser</li>
        <li><strong>Export/Import:</strong> Copy to clipboard for spreadsheets</li>
        <li><strong>Over/Under & Implied Points:</strong> Additional betting insights</li>
        <li><strong>Mobile Friendly:</strong> Works on all devices</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded-lg p-6 mb-8">
